Ishay Davidi: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 7:19 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of First Israel Mezzanine Investors Ltd.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Ishay   Davidi  Founder, Chief Executive Officer, and Chairman, First Israel Mezzanine Investors Ltd.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 12 Board Members in 12 different organizations across 21 different industries.See Board Relationships55--
Background

		Mr. Ishay Davidi founded First Israel Mezzanine Investors Ltd., in 1996 and has been its Chief Executive Officer since 1996. Mr. Davidi is the Founder, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at FIMI Opportunity Fund I, L.P., FIMI V and FIMI Opportunity II, L.P. He is the Chief Executive Officer and Senior Partner of FIMI Fund. He serves as General Manager at First Israel. He is a Co-Founder of First Israel Turnaround Enterprise Fund. He held senior management positions ... in a variety of leading Israeli industrial and high-tech companies. From 1992 to 1993 Mr. Davidi served as the Chief Executive Officer of Zer Science Industries Ltd. He served as the Chief Executive Officer at Tikvah VC Fund and served as the Chief Executive Officer at two Israeli industrial companies. He serves as Chairman of First Israel Mezzanine Investors Ltd. He serves as Chairman of Hadera Paper Ltd. He has been Chairman of Inrom Construction Industries Ltd. since January 2014. He served as the Chairman of Ormat Industries Ltd. at Ormat Technologies Inc. He served as the Chairman of Retalix Ltd. from August 2008 to January 2010 and First Israel Turnaround Enterprise. Mr. Davidi served as the Chairman of Tadir-Gan. He served as the Chairman of Tefron Ltd. from November 2005 to December 2007 and served as its Director since June 2005. He has been a Director of Overseas Commerce Ltd. since June 2013, Retalix Ltd. since March 2008 and Gilat Satellite Networks Ltd. since December 31, 2012. He serves as a Director of Novolog (Pharm-Up Marketing (1966) Ltd)., Novolog (Pharm-Up 1922) Ltd., and Rekah Pharmaceutical Industries. He has been Director of Ham-Let (Israel Canada) Ltd since August 15, 2012 and Rekah Pharmaceutical Industry Ltd., since April 15, 2015. He serves as a Director of Inrom Industries Ltd., Inrom Construction Industries Ltd., Poliram Plastic Industries Ltd. Hadera Pepper Ltd., Tadir-Gan Exact Products Ltd., H. Mar Industries Ltd., Norfet Limited Partnership, Tadiran Communications, Tedea Technological Development and Automation Ltd., TG Precision Products Ltd., Orlite Industries 1959 Ltd., MDT Micro Diamond Technologies Ltd., Orian Nv, Bagir Group Ltd., Medtechnica Ltd., and Merhav Building Materials and Ceramic Center Ltd. He has been Director at Tadir-Gan (Precision Products) 1993 Ltd. since 2016. He served as a Director at Orian Sh.M. Ltd. He served as a Director of Lipman Electronic Engineering Ltd. since September 2002. Mr. Davidi served as a Director of B.G.I. Investments (1961) Ltd, Hamat Group Ltd and Gamatronic Electronic Industries, Ltd. He served as a Director of C. Mer Industries Ltd., since October 15, 2013 and Scope Metals Group Ltd. since 2006 until September 2013. He served as a Director of Ormat Industries Ltd. and Formula Systems (1985) Ltd. since March 2005. He served as a Director of TAT Technologies, Ltd., since September 1, 2004 and Ophir Optronics Ltd. He holds BSc Degree in Industrial Engineering & Management from Tel Aviv University. Mr. Davidi holds MBA in Finance from Bar Ilan University.Read Full Background




